  "detailed_description": "Retro Rally! is a top-down racing game where classic arcade racing meets modern excitement. Race head-to-head in local co-op Circuit Mode or test your speed in challenging time trials. Championship races and a high-stakes Gauntlet Mode await. Get ready for a nostalgic, adrenaline-pumping journey back to classic arcade gaming.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669620/extras/1c85cdf70ab525d917efd1a1a935561b.poster.avif?t=1739595389\" width=442 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669620/extras/1c85cdf70ab525d917efd1a1a935561b.webm?t=1739595389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669620/extras/1c85cdf70ab525d917efd1a1a935561b.mp4?t=1739595389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Local Multiplayer</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Up to 4 player local multiplayer<br></li><li> Race head-to-head in circuit mode</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669620/extras/ea58e7e5cbf0ba1dd1ea5236cde1d8e9.poster.avif?t=1739595389\" width=578 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669620/extras/ea58e7e5cbf0ba1dd1ea5236cde1d8e9.webm?t=1739595389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669620/extras/ea58e7e5cbf0ba1dd1ea5236cde1d8e9.mp4?t=1739595389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Circuit Mode</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 4 standard circuits<br></li><li> 4 unlock-able reverse circuits<br></li><li> Supports 4 player local multiplayer or single player vs 3 AI</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669620/extras/66bfaa0829d95cc976e0b1aa8d6424e5.avif?t=1739595389\" width=550 height=306 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Time Trial Mode</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 16 tracks<br></li><li> 16 unlock-able reverse tracks<br></li><li> Bronze, silver and gold medal challenge times</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gauntlet Mode</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Standard gauntlet mode (cycles the normal tracks)<br></li><li> Random gauntlet mode (randomizes the track order)<br></li><li> Race until you lose (AI increases in difficulty as you progress)<br></li><li> Collect money and upgrade your car to keep up!<br></li><li> Rack up a high score with money and race time bonuses</li></ul>",
