b_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669620/extras/66bfaa0829d95cc976e0b1aa8d6424e5.avif?t=1739595389\" width=550 height=306 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Time Trial Mode</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 16 tracks<br></li><li> 16 unlock-able reverse tracks<br></li><li> Bronze, silver and gold medal challenge times</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gauntlet Mode</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Standard gauntlet mode (cycles the normal tracks)<br></li><li> Random gauntlet mode (randomizes the track order)<br></li><li> Race until you lose (AI increases in difficulty as you progress)<br></li><li> Collect money and upgrade your car to keep up!<br></li><li> Rack up a high score with money and race time bonuses</li></ul>",
